Parliament, Wednesday, 21 October 2020 – A delegation of the Ad Hoc Committee to Initiate and Introduce Legislation Amending Section 25 of the Constitution in order to allow for the expropriation of land without compensation will tomorrow, 22 October, begin public hearings in Limpopo Province.
	
	Details of the hearings:  Limpopo 22 October 11:00 Vhembe Makwarela Community Hall ISSUED BY THE PARLIAMENTARY COMMUNICATION SERVICES 
	
	For media enquiries or interviews regarding the Limpopo leg of the public hearings, please contact the Committee’s Media Officer:
	Name: Rajaa Azzakani (Ms)
